Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.53,0:00:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我知道了～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.34,0:00:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}紅緒在嫉妒白夜對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.37,0:00:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嫉妒？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.70,0:00:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅和白夜很恩愛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.75,0:00:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以不高興了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.88,0:00:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}對吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.09,0:00:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}得意的樣子也很可愛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.08,0:00:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}才沒問你那種事情！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.27,0:00:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}才、才沒有很恩愛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.21,0:00:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而且早就有婚約了現在才這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.18,0:00:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是啊 說不定是為時已晚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.22,0:01:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.91,0:01:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}重新思考過一次之後
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.41,0:01:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}果然超級不愉快的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.58,0:01:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}婚約？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.88,0:01:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我才不管呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.87,0:01:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅是我的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.22,0:01:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}才不會讓給其他人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.12,0:01:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你是小孩子嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.05,0:01:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H90532F&\shad0\bord3\pos(1163,447)\fad(270,0)}紅\N緒\N視\N角
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.81,0:01:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個臉是啥啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.57,0:01:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊啊啊 冷靜點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.72,0:01:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}總之老娘就是不爽啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.53,0:01:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是的 事到如今了還鬧什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.27,0:01:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}白夜也說句話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.88,0:01:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}父…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.35,0:01:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}父親嗎你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.36,0:01:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吐槽？！
Dialogue: 1,0:03:16.42,0:03:21.38,title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(480,470)}#10 查了一下嬌羞期這個詞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.42,0:03:21.38,title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(480,470)\3c&HF2C855&\bord7}#10 查了一下嬌羞期這個詞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.28,0:03:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\an8}我是不會說不能原諒之類的話的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.90,0:03:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}畢竟白夜是小紅的救命恩人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.44,0:03:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是我要告訴你我非常不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.84,0:03:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}還有 我把真白碳當成是自己的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.18,0:03:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以說這是兩件事情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.08,0:03:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什麼啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.04,0:03:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這是哪門子的任性啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.46,0:03:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}呃 不要在意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.16,0:03:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}才不會在意呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.71,0:03:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要是事事都在意的話早就受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.98,0:03:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雖然說了不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.51,0:04:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是把真白當做妹妹？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.25,0:04:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啥意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.05,0:04:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以說不用那麼認真的聽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.06,0:04:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}究竟怎麼回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.82,0:04:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我跟白夜又沒有什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.95,0:04:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.34,0:04:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.53,0:04:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.45,0:04:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.43,0:04:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以說紅緒心情差是因為小紅喜歡白夜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.30,0:04:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一定是這樣的吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.94,0:04:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我才沒有這樣說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.86,0:04:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}差不多就相當於說了一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.71,0:04:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我只是說我不會排斥婚約啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.75,0:04:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只有這樣而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.66,0:04:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 這麼說…就連這個也…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.49,0:04:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不爽呢 一定是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.03,0:04:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}紅緒的事情先丟一邊去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.84,0:04:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}比起那個你們白色情人節該怎麼弄呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.23,0:04:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}靠近眼前的問題是這個才是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.75,0:04:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不 沒有禮物也沒關係的啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.86,0:05:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我跟白夜又沒有什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.09,0:05:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不可以在意紅緒的事情喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.26,0:05:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我只有說我不會排斥婚約啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.99,0:05:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}乾脆把手牽起來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.64,0:05:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}來來 就像這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.62,0:05:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這、這個是…
Dialogue: 1,0:05:23.67,0:05:27.17,sc,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs70\fsp5\c&HBD6D1C&\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(1174,364)\fad(1600,0)}終\N於\N活\N抓
Dialogue: 1,0:05:23.67,0:05:27.17,sc,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1600,0)\bord0\fs70\fsp5\pos(821,70)}創世紀的證據照片
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.67,0:05:27.17,sc,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1600,0)\bord0\c&HB3281C&\fscx2000\fscy300\pos(802,86)}▆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.21,0:05:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早、早
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.53,0:05:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}還是該說早安呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.40,0:05:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅就拜託你囉 未續
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.82,0:05:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要怎麼搭話才好呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.36,0:05:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 這個是
Dialogue: 1,0:05:46.99,0:05:50.24,sc,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\fs70\fsp5\pos(681,72)}獨家新聞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.99,0:05:50.24,sc,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\fscx1200\fscy250\pos(666,79)\c&H262BDC&}▆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.51,0:05:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小不點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.19,0:05:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個 未續同學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.49,0:06:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}等等方便打擾一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.47,0:06:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.43,0:06:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}蛋糕？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.66,0:06:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.76,0:06:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}昨天給你添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.95,0:06:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就當做賠罪的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.06,0:06:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}謝、謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.93,0:06:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明明是我把她弄哭的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.86,0:06:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我跟姐姐大人不同
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.62,0:06:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不太擅長站在很多人面前受到注目
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.39,0:06:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只是覺得因為婚約的事情被說閒話會很難受
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.35,0:06:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但也不是說討厭婚約這件事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.48,0:06:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.95,0:06:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}木葉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.34,0:06:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.35,0:06:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊勒 蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.64,0:06:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好像很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.62,0:06:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}還沒開始就要結束了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.57,0:06:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.86,0:07:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}抱歉 我今天值日所以晚到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.21,0:07:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.36,0:07:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真香
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.83,0:07:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個…會長怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.14,0:07:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}妹妹和未婚夫關係要好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.90,0:07:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}事到如今才開始不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.96,0:07:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這有點說不出口呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.17,0:07:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在注視著自己的內在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.47,0:07:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}未續也要來杯茶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.16,0:07:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.67,0:07:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}對了 收到的蛋糕…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.73,0:07:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哎呀 那不是小紅做的蛋糕嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.54,0:08:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 啊 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.57,0:08:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這都被看出來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.21,0:08:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}剛才從您妹妹那裡收到的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.00,0:08:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哎呀 有和她好好相處呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.34,0:08:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.25,0:08:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是 是！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.86,0:08:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 兩位要不要嚐嚐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.02,0:08:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雖然只是點小東西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.72,0:08:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小東西？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.52,0:08:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}末續 冷靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.10,0:08:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但也不是說討厭婚約這件事情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.77,0:08:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.00,0:08:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一開始這麼說不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.43,0:08:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}弄得我像個笨蛋一樣不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.39,0:08:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}她說討厭被說閒話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.04,0:08:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我怎麼可能會到處說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.03,0:08:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}木葉 有什麼好的題材嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.15,0:08:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}獨家報導 獨家報導……
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.79,0:08:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 果然不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.94,0:08:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}的確沒辦法跟身為仁子醬朋友的我開口呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.05,0:09:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個…白夜同學怎麼了呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.25,0:09:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}發生好事了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.30,0:09:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好事？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.33,0:09:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}噢 那個是這樣的表情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.14,0:09:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}和小紅的好感度升級了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.25,0:09:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.43,0:09:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}太好了呢 白夜同學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.67,0:09:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個…我和小紅是正式情侶？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.69,0:09:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.11,0:09:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}末續同學會吃我的蛋糕嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.98,0:09:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅是我老婆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.65,0:09:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什！？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.58,0:09:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嘛 是這回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.44,0:09:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因為是未婚夫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.16,0:09:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\an3}你們在說啥！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.47,0:09:45.72,EX,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\c&H48050D&}嬌羞期（又名dr期）\N\N\N\N「嬌羞期」是指對特定的對象抱有好感，\N並被其萌倒的時期。比如喜歡上特定的偶\N像團體或演員而變得輕飄飄的時候就會公\N開「嬌羞期來了！」之類的發言。\N嬌羞期來臨的同時，會喚起對特定對象言\N行的強烈好感，即使在周圍來看是古怪的\N事件也會使本人萌發出更多的好感。越來\N越看不清身邊的事物…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.25,0:09:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}查了一下嬌羞期這個詞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.50,0:09:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就有了這些說明
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.14,0:09:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以不是說這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.93,0:09:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我覺得對白夜做了好多失禮的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.81,0:09:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}想要道歉之類的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.25,0:10:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅醬好認真呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.58,0:10:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}白夜對那種事情完全沒有在意哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.11,0:10:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}失禮……是說啥事？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.40,0:10:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒…那個……
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.89,0:10:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}應該說是我的感覺的問題…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.62,0:10:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嘛 總之
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.07,0:10:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果嬌羞了的話那就按嬌羞的那樣拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.44,0:10:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以說不是這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.41,0:10:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那麼…之後就交給兩位年輕人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.68,0:10:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}礙事的人就消失好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.22,0:10:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.27,0:10:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}說出了約定俗成的台詞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.41,0:10:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一直想要說一次看看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.11,0:10:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.19,0:10:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那麼 總之
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.46,0:10:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什 什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.26,0:10:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}總之回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.42,0:10:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哦 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.42,0:11:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.47,0:11:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我可以偶爾給小紅發郵件嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.34,0:11:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.32,0:11:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 這麼快
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.15,0:11:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為 為什麼這麼快就兩個人回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.99,0:11:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真白碳怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.77,0:11:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真白碳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.31,0:11:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也就是說現在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.98,0:11:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真白碳是野生的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.95,0:11:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一個人？單獨一個人回家！？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.61,0:11:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 危險
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.92,0:11:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}回家的時候大家要結伴回家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.44,0:11:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.95,0:11:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}從二樓跳下來沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.39,0:12:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒事 因為我運動神經很好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.35,0:12:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這是運動神經好就能辦到的事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.81,0:12:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}讓真白碳一個人回家很危險的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.77,0:12:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.74,0:12:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你在搗什麼亂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.10,0:12:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊呀 真白碳你在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.41,0:12:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}紅緒是搗蛋鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.93,0:12:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}去 去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.27,0:12:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好久沒有被叫搗蛋鬼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.33,0:12:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.81,0:12:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這人根本沒在聽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.37,0:12:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也就是說你們兩個都躲著看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.17,0:12:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}對 對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.36,0:12:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是果然有種放不下的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.04,0:12:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}木葉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.33,0:12:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 仁子醬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.74,0:12:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}木葉你是學生會的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.86,0:12:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有沒有從紅緒大人那裡聽到小紅的事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.58,0:13:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}能不能成為新聞的素材呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.92,0:13:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哦 還在取材嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.31,0:13:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}她本人好像不怎麼喜歡顯眼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.59,0:13:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}仁子醬 我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.08,0:13:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不是沒有題材呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.02,0:13:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.34,0:13:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.62,0:13:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.51,0:13:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}新的牆報上寫著小紅的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.91,0:13:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦！？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.19,0:13:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}寫了點什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.92,0:13:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這八成左右都是紅緒的報導不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.75,0:13:41.25,sc,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H423D4C&\frz22.503\pos(614,176)\3c&HF7FCFB&}紅緒大人的降臨!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.91,0:13:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}木葉 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.90,0:13:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}第一次通過審查呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.58,0:13:52.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不用謝 能幫上仁子醬太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.47,0:13:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\3c&HE8ECEE&\pos(883,544)\c&H4A2A4B&}紅\N緒\N大\N人\N的\N妹\N妹\N很\N擅\N長\N料\N理
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.61,0:13:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這一點的題材沒關係的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.98,0:14:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哎呀 小紅被寫上校內新聞了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.75,0:14:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.80,0:14:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要切下來保存才好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.58,0:14:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}住手吧你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.16,0:14:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.42,0:14:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅不喜歡這樣的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.92,0:14:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我本來以為那種程度沒有關係的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.74,0:14:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}難道說讓紅緒大人生氣了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.84,0:14:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是啊 上新聞之後小紅的可愛之處廣為人知
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.30,0:14:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}被奇怪的蟲子盯上可就糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.24,0:14:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嘛 那個時候我不吭聲可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.91,0:14:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}太近了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.52,0:14:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}做了多餘的事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.79,0:14:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}木葉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.89,0:15:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}回頭一想這新聞算不上獨家報導！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.91,0:15:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}被發現了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.70,0:15:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.56,0:15:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}末續同學對白夜說了結婚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.19,0:15:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}她是…喜歡白夜的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.63,0:15:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.78,0:15:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只是因為同族而已哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.16,0:15:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎麼會有這麼簡單…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.61,0:15:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}的事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.97,0:15:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}似乎被母親告知一旦發現同族就要先佔有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.92,0:15:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}佔有?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.73,0:15:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}確實同族不怎麼容易看到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.50,0:15:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.35,0:15:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅也有一半像是同族一樣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.22,0:15:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.87,0:15:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 為什麼我會
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.01,0:15:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊勒 沒跟你說過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.96,0:15:55.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}白夜給了你一半的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.15,0:15:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以小紅你也算是我們一半的夥伴了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.97,0:16:05.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那 就是說我也具有什麼不可思議的能力嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.44,0:16:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}撒 倒也不至於那麼夢幻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.51,0:16:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這麼說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.18,0:16:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}末續同學的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.52,0:16:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我就不用那麼介意了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.51,0:16:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不用介意不用介意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.37,0:16:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那麼失禮的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.96,0:16:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我們還不想搭理她呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.76,0:16:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}火大！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.91,0:16:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以說你就安心的跟白夜好好相處吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.95,0:16:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大膽的穿情侶裝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.49,0:16:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我才不
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.36,0:16:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.00,0:16:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}姐姐 你是什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.14,0:16:41.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 我也是才到的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.41,0:16:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在說情侶裝的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.76,0:16:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}太好了 末續同學跟真白她們是同族的事沒被聽見
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.93,0:16:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我倒是跟小紅穿過情侶裝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.05,0:16:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我贏了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.77,0:16:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你說的是小時候的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.77,0:16:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那時好可愛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.71,0:16:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雖然買過好多套
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.16,0:17:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是我最喜歡的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.64,0:17:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不會的不會的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.68,0:17:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}下次要跟真白碳穿情侶裝哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.22,0:17:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你少開玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.51,0:17:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&H5864EC&\shad0}我 跟小紅 有什麼一樣的東西…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.39,0:17:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}對了 我想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.69,0:17:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}白色情人節的禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.29,0:17:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}送一個能跟你成對的東西就好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.96,0:17:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這麼說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.33,0:17:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真白碳也要對我回禮哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.88,0:17:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}白色情人節那天
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.52,0:17:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不要 這是兩件事情好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.80,0:17:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}能配成對的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.93,0:17:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}果然還是印有名字首字母的毛衣或者圍巾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.81,0:17:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不要不要不要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.36,0:17:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}都已經是春天了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.26,0:17:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}已經轉暖的說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.64,0:17:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我不會織
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.53,0:17:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而且手織嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.11,0:17:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}糟糕 我也不會織
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.07,0:18:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}姐姐大人也不用和他對抗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.38,0:18:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什麼配對啊 什麼白色情人節的就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.87,0:18:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而且為什麼關係好就等於要配對呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.91,0:18:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不會弄的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.06,0:18:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}應該說不行的
