Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.70,0:18:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}從剛才開始一直在查什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.92,0:18:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今天回去的時候我有點事要做
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.67,0:18:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}分開行動
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.84,0:18:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有事？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.74,0:18:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是稀奇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.99,0:18:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再見
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.29,0:18:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.49,0:18:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我們可以回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.37,0:19:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}白夜說的有事是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.69,0:19:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這不明擺著的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.64,0:19:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}肯定是去找白色情人節要送的禮物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.97,0:19:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就那麼想試試嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.27,0:19:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}情侶裝什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.02,0:19:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是被紅緒鼓動的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.48,0:19:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}想要一個能用形狀體現和小紅感情的東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.92,0:19:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 白夜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.24,0:19:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}事情處理好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.29,0:19:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我們談談好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.58,0:20:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}手帕…雖然是顏色不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.93,0:20:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是跟我的是配對的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.08,0:20:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}配對
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.07,0:20:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}佛光！？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.80,0:20:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊咧 白夜你辦完事了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.86,0:20:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你看看 這個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.58,0:20:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}出巧克力蛋UMA系列第二彈了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.10,0:20:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}出新品了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.49,0:20:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這是屈斜路湖的庫希
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.98,0:20:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}狂熱的程度又提高了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.20,0:20:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個…這個事情對大家要保密的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.06,0:20:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不是我不願意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.19,0:20:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只是被姐姐大人知道了的話就不得了了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.06,0:20:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.16,0:20:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為什麼被我知道就不得了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.48,0:20:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.60,0:20:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}禮物嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.12,0:20:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有點噁心想吐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.14,0:20:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎麼回事！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.24,0:21:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.53,0:21:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}壓力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.37,0:21:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}說被我知道了就不得了是為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.80,0:21:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就是會這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.56,0:21:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}白夜那是什麼啊 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.19,0:21:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.25,0:21:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什麼嘛什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.99,0:21:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}快告訴我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.29,0:21:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個…本打算回去的時候給你們的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.36,0:21:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}來 姐姐和真白的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.66,0:21:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}手帕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.31,0:21:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}UMA系列第二彈、手帕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.15,0:21:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今天真是個好日子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.10,0:21:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是被小紅搶先了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.93,0:21:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這樣一來要送更加有氣勢的禮物才行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.76,0:21:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雖然那麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.64,0:21:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不要氣餒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.39,0:21:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}跟小紅的關係能不能相處好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.27,0:21:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}請做好現在就是關鍵時期的覺悟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.08,0:21:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}壓力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.41,0:21:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}加油 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.00,0:00:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}ED
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.46,0:23:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}UMA系列第二彈
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.31,0:23:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}從池田湖的伊西 蘆之湖的阿西
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.14,0:23:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}到洞爺湖的同西 都集全了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.10,0:23:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊～真白碳 還有紅緒緒呢哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.16,0:23:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這週也出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.24,0:23:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那 我就是小紅紅了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.74,0:23:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}下集
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.86,0:23:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}很喜歡手帕哦

